    "Description": "XenoThreat recently hit a Headhunters' stronghold. I\u2019ll spare you the details, but they did some truly heinous shit to our crew. We\u2019ve identified the leader of the op as ~mission(TargetName) and are looking for a little payback. We don\u2019t care what you do to get the job done. Only that ~mission(TargetName|Last) is dead. \n\nA source just told us that you can track down this XenoThreat scum over at ~mission(Location|Address). This sicko\u2019s a pro and never travels alone, so don\u2019t expect taking them out to be a walk in the park.  \n\nStows out.",
